flowchart TD
  U[User] --> P[Planner (LLM): propose action JSON]
  P --> E[Executor (Deterministic): schema validate
extra=forbid + guardrails]
  E -->|valid| TA[Tool Adapters]
  E -->|invalid| R1[Reject + ask for correction]
  TA --> S[Domain Services]
  S --> R[Repositories]
  R --> DB[(PostgreSQL/DB)]
  E --> O[Observability: logs/traces/outcomes]
  E --> C[Confidence + Critic (optional, separate model)]
  C --> P
  O --> U
  S --> U
